      <title>LeetCode:从排序数组中删除重复项</title>
      <link>http://www.godlikemeteor.com/2018/07/04/LeetCode-%E4%BB%8E%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%8D%E9%A1%B9/</link>
